{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"abec166aac","title":"用袭击方法夺取洪洞赵城","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9747ab1e13","index":0,"year":1946,"month":8,"day":6,"articleId":"abec166aac"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"445cf0d29b","type":"paragraph","text":"用袭击方法夺取洪洞赵城","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"abec166aac"},{"id":"79bf5e389d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年8月6日）陈、谢：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"abec166aac"},{"id":"83ab8a832f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）你们对洪赵应先行侦察，然后秘密运动部队，用袭击方法夺取之，不使胡军事前知道。（二）主力北上攻洪赵，闻喜附近是否应留一部钳制胡军？（三）部队已休整好否，何日可开始行动","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"abec166aac"},{"id":"7817751f53","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"abec166aac"},{"id":"38457d1a8d","type":"paragraph","text":"未鱼[1]这是毛泽东为中共中夹军委起草的给晋冀鲁豫野战军第四纵队司令员陈愿和政治委员谢富治的电报。[2]洪赵，指洪洞、赵城，均为旧县名，1954年两县合并为山西洪赵县，1958年改为山西洪洞县。[3]胡军，指国民党军第一战区司令长官胡宗南部整编第一师、第二十七师。该两师当时位于山西闻喜、夏县地区。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"abec166aac"}],"page":{"id":"dc19cf6bfa","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"abec166aac","start":42,"end":42}}}},"__N_SSG":true}